  (text "POWER + CAN (docs/09 s.3): bus tap through 2A mini fuse -> LMR36015 -> 5V0 ->\nNCP1117 -> 3V3 (vetted Phase-1 chain, single ground). 3V3 feeds the backplane\nE-stop pull-up via J1.10: unplugged manager = all modules SAFE. Q8 = manager\nE-stop assert (open-drain); no CAN termination here (backplane owns both ends)." (at 25.4 33.02 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c3183f65-d25a-4382-bf23-913d232feb7a))
